I have made this cake literally a hundred times since receiving the magazine issue in which it was first published. Yummmmy! I use peaches in the summer, and have also used other fruits including pears, plums, and a combination of nectarines and other fruits. I can't believe five ingredients can produce such a delicious cake. I am addicted-if I bake this delight when I am having a sweet tooth moment, usually late at night, other household members are lucky to even get a taste of this beauty, the following day...

