Rating: 3
This was fantastic, even as breakfast! To modify it for breakfast fare, I split the batter into muffin cups, reduced the butter and the sugar, and used some whole-wheat flour. The cake itself is fabulous due to the lemon flavor, and this is well complemented by the cinnamon/nectarine combination for good balance. I'd recommend this even in muffin form for a quick early breakfast! (In muffin pan, cooked ~20 min at 400 degrees)

