Rating: 3
Like most everyone here, I had to change a few things; 3 nectarines were plenty; All-purpose flour/2tsp baking powder/1/2tsp salt instead of self rising flour; Sprinkling the cake with all the sugar/cinnamon at the end was not necessary, cut it to 1/3 of that and add just a touch of clove; please, serve with ginger whipped cream. You can use any stone fruit on hand.

